song_name: Ballad Of The Self Loading Pistol

version_description: I figured it's about time there was a half decent effort at this.
Based on the VH1 Storytellers version.
The tab is on 2nd fret while other versions are with no capo.
Ver 6 was missing verse 2. Chords: Updated, complete and formatted. added section headings. Correct key, G, and easier key to play.
